What say you?

978
01:26:11,834 --> 01:26:17,088
我們一致認為  原告穆麗兒·蘭太太勝訴
We rule in favor of the plaintiff, Mrs. Muriel Lang, on all counts.

979
01:26:18,090 --> 01:26:22,510
法庭對陪審團在這困難的情況下所作的努力表示感謝
The court would like to thank the jury for its service in this difficult case.

980
01:26:22,678 --> 01:26:25,429
退庭
Court is dismissed.

981
01:26:47,953 --> 01:26:51,289
- 關於你和伊芳的通姦  - 別再侮辱她
- About the reports of Yvonne's adultery-- - Shut up about her.

982
01:26:51,456 --> 01:26:53,207
她在下面
She's down there.

983
01:26:55,502 --> 01:26:57,628
伊芳
Yvonne!

984
01:27:06,179 --> 01:27:08,306
伊芳
Yvonne!

985
01:27:10,809 --> 01:27:13,686
- 蘭太太  你對裁決有什麼看法  - 非常公正
