有人在嗎
Is anyone here?

996
01:30:18,830 --> 01:30:20,664
走吧
Go away.

997
01:30:21,666 --> 01:30:23,167
伊芳
Yvonne.

998
01:30:23,335 --> 01:30:27,838
- 不  你不會想再和我在一起的  - 你說什麼呢
- No. You don't wanna be with me. - What are you talking about?

999
01:30:31,009 --> 01:30:35,596
- 我愛你  - 不  你還不明白嗎
- I love you. - No. Don't you get it?

1000
01:30:35,847 --> 01:30:37,181
我毀了你的生活
I've ruined your life.

1001
01:30:37,349 --> 01:30:42,853
你瘋了嗎  沒有你在的這些日子  我感覺自己像丟了魂似的
Are you crazy? These past couple of days, I felt like half of me was missing.

1002
01:30:43,230 --> 01:30:49,693
你中了四百萬美元啊  你知道這是多麼驚人的一份厚禮嗎
You won $4 million in the lottery. Do you know what an amazing gift that is?

1003
01:30:49,861 --> 01:30:53,030
而現在  因為我  你什麼都沒有了
And because of me you have nothing.

1004
01:30:53,198 --> 01:30:57,952
正是因為你  我愛你  難道你還不明白嗎
Because of you, I have you. Why can't you understand that?

1005
01:30:59,788 --> 01:31:01,914
如果你不想要我  這是另一回事
If you don't want me, that's different.

1006
01:31:02,082 --> 01:31:06,377
如果你不要我  我會走出這道門  你永遠都不會再見到我
If you don't want me, I'll walk right out that door, and you'll never see me again.

1007
01:31:06,545 --> 01:31:12,550
但是別再說什麼錢  錢對我沒有任何意義
But please stop talking about the money. It means nothing to me.

1008
01:31:19,975 --> 01:31:21,100
你希望我走嗎
Do you want me to go?

1009
01:31:27,274 --> 01:31:29,024
不
No.

1010
01:31:33,238 --> 01:31:34,238
永遠不
Never.

1011
01:31:37,075 --> 01:31:38,576
永遠別走  永遠
Never, never.

1012
01:31:44,583 --> 01:31:47,626
有些時候你該原諒我  因為
You have to excuse me sometimes, it's just...

1013
01:31:48,336 --> 01:31:51,380
從來沒有人這樣愛過我
...nobody ever loved me before.

1014
01:32:25,123 --> 01:32:30,044
- 我想他可能想找點吃的  - 我們讓他進來吧
- I guess he wants some food. - Shall we invite him in?

1015
01:32:32,005 --> 01:32:33,339
為什麼不呢
Why not?

1016
01:32:56,154 --> 01:32:58,530
我們應該離開紐約
We should leave New York.

1017
01:33:01,034 --> 01:33:03,535
我的意思是  我們在這裏都成怪物了
I mean, we're like freaks here.

1018
01:33:06,873 --> 01:33:10,960
我有個遠親住在水牛城
I've got a cousin that lives in Buffalo.

1019
01:33:11,127 --> 01:33:13,504
他一直叫我過去
He keeps asking me to visit.

1020
01:33:14,506 --> 01:33:17,132
也許我們可以在那兒呆上一陣子
Maybe we can stay there for a while.

1021
01:33:17,968 --> 01:33:20,594
我可以在水牛城當警察
I could join the Buffalo force.

1022
01:33:23,848 --> 01:33:26,976
我可以在水牛城做女招待
I could be a Buffalo waitress.

1023
01:33:43,660 --> 01:33:48,789
今晚  我  安吉爾·杜普裏  一個從業十年的紐約郵報攝影記者
Tonight I, Angel Dupree, a photographer for the New York Post for 10 years...

1024
01:33:48,957 --> 01:33:55,045
有機會在惡劣的天氣裏  感受到什麼是真正的樂善好施
...had the opportunity to study grace and generosity under the direst of circumstances.

1025
01:33:56,800 --> 01:33:58,000
「紐約郵報」

1026
01:33:58,640 --> 01:34:00,860
「黑暗時刻的溫情」

1027
01:34:00,969 --> 01:34:06,056
即使他們非常困難  這位勇敢的蘭警官和好心腸的比亞西小姐
Even in their darkest hour, the stalwart Officer Lang and the good-hearted Miss Biasi...

1028
01:34:06,224 --> 01:34:08,851
仍然讓我享受了一碗美味的熱湯
...shared a bowl of soup with me.

1029
01:34:09,894 --> 01:34:14,148
臨走時  這位好心人還從他口袋裏掏錢給我
When I left, this Good Samaritan gave me money from his own pocket...

1030
01:34:14,357 --> 01:34:16,984
還希望我別嫌少
...wishing it could be more.

1031
01:34:17,152 --> 01:34:22,573
- 請寄往摩爾北街  伊芳咖啡館  - 這是一個好主意
- "Mail it to Yvonne's Coffee Shop." - It's a good idea.

1032
01:34:22,741 --> 01:34:24,074
這個主意棒極了
It's a great idea.

1033
01:34:32,250 --> 01:34:34,626
我就看一眼
I just want to make one stop.

1034
01:34:39,841 --> 01:34:43,427
- 親愛的  - 我挺好  我挺好
- Sweetie. - I'm okay, I'm okay.

1035
01:34:43,678 --> 01:34:48,140
- 我看這樣不太好  - 沒關係  我只是想再看看
- I knew this was a bad idea. - No, I just wanted to see it again.

1036
01:34:48,308 --> 01:34:50,434
門怎麼開了
Why is the gate open?

1037
01:34:51,895 --> 01:34:56,607
我不知道  嗯  卡洛兒有鑰匙
I don't know. Well, Carol has a key.

1038
01:34:57,400 --> 01:34:59,610
門被頂住了
The door's stuck.

1039
01:35:08,036 --> 01:35:11,997
- 這是什麼  - 誰弄錯了吧
- What is this? - It must be some kind of a mistake.

1040
01:35:12,165 --> 01:35:16,794
- 好撒瑪利亞人關懷基金  - 彩票情侶
- "The Good Samaritan's Fund." - "Lotto Lovers."

1041
01:35:16,961 --> 01:35:19,296
寄給伊芳咖啡館
"Yvonne's Coffee Shop."

1042
01:35:22,884 --> 01:35:26,804
- 這兒有五美元  - 噢  怎麼回事  不對吧
- It's 5 dollars. - Oh, come on. No.

1043
01:35:26,971 --> 01:35:32,976
世上應該有越來越多像你們這樣的人  斯泰登島  艾瑟兒寄
"There should be more people in the world like you. Ethel from Staten Island."

1044
01:35:36,314 --> 01:35:38,524
這是一張十美元的支票
Here's a check for 10.

1045
